title: Kanykayevo
content:
Kanykayevo (Russian: Каныкаево; Bashkir: Ҡаныҡай, Qanıqay) is a rural locality (a selo) in Bikkulovsky Selsoviet, Bizhbulyaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 360 as of 2010.[2] There are 7 streets.

Kanykayevo is located 37 km southwest of Bizhbulyak (the district's administrative centre) by road. Bikkulovo is the nearest rural locality.[3]
